title: DAZ3D - LY Fallon for Genesis 3 Female(s)
description:
Fallon has the elegance of a woman who knows her worth and has a touch of darkness in her. Beautiful looks that run to the gothic style, she can grace any room and easily be the center of attention.

Many hours of loving attention went into the skin. The skin was creating from high-res photos, no merchant resources were used. All the textures use the Genesis 3 Female UV. Options include eight eye colors plus, eight makeups/lipsticks and nine nail designs. As always, there are eleven presets that include makeup, nails, and lips for an easy all-in-one solution.
